# Haskell WATs

This is a collection of Haskell's WATs

## Eq Double

```
Prelude> let nan = read "NaN" :: Double
Prelude> nan == nan
False
Prelude> nan /= nan
True
```

## Ord Double

```
Prelude> let nan = read "NaN" :: Double
Prelude> nan >= nan
False
Prelude> nan > nan
False
Prelude> nan <= nan
False
Prelude> nan < nan
False
Prelude> compare nan nan
GT
```

## Real Double

``` Haskell
Prelude> let nan = read "NaN" :: Double
Prelude> toRational nan
(-) % 1
Prelude> realToFrac nan -- With -O0
-Infinity
Prelude> realToFrac nan
NaN
```

## RealFrac Double

```
Prelude> let nan = read "NaN" :: Double
Prelude> properFraction nan
(-,0.0)
truncate nan
-
Prelude> round nan
-
Prelude> floor nan
-
Prelude> ceiling nan
-
```
